{"id": "1426523827449626745", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：永无乡假日 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日\n有一个地方只能在仲夏夜梦境中到达，那是我们得以重聚的永无乡。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Neverland Holiday\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST: Neverland Holiday\nThere's one place that can only be reached within a Midsummer Night's Dream—a Neverland where we can finally meet again.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:56:23.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "H_immerse", "emoji_id": "1426122347643146250", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1426523828154138665", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2117670, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426523828154138665/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69ccf9d8&is=69cba858&hm=da24d95b3389fd60ac45d75e5902aa3ca5acf4f5d4b49f14e1a3bc092b0ef90c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426523988187676733", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 伦蒂尼恩之夏-Summer in Londinium-**\n\n我们为您准备了一个完美的假期，包括沙滩、阳光、排球赛，旧朋友和新朋友。\n请务必做好防晒，如果太阳从天空坠落，不用惊慌失措，这是正常现象。\n\nWe've prepared you a perfect holiday! There're beaches, sunshine, volleyball matches, old and new friends…\nBe sure to pack sunscreen, and if you see the sun falling, please don't panic—it's quite natural, actually.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:57:02.318000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426523987466256395", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1457387, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426523987466256395/1.jpg?ex=69ccf9fe&is=69cba87e&hm=3d6682f80c5671131d6345c03f6acec232d47bab94cfe7969e198c084e5de908&"}, {"id": "1426523987776897034", "filename": "01._-Summer_in_Londinium-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19838096, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426523987776897034/01._-Summer_in_Londinium-.wav?ex=69ccf9fe&is=69cba87e&hm=a4395b10d21084cc4bf095e12eb13ba95cf43ad804404505af5ac2f31f69ffee&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426524052469583984", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 独角剧目-A Monodrama-**\n\n她坚持要单独出演，否则就要给你一枪。\n但最后她获得了一位好学生，还有一匹狼。\n\nShe insisted on performing alone, or she'd put a bullet in you.\nAnyway, she ended up with a good student and a wolf in row.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:57:17.644000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426524051546832966", "filename": "02._-A_Monodrama-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20678908, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524051546832966/02._-A_Monodrama-.wav?ex=69ccfa0d&is=69cba88d&hm=2b585f15235d7abcab89718d0eac05e9d4f949193dd40bdc4e8a1b307e9033cd&"}, {"id": "1426524052100747406", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1442219, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524052100747406/2.jpg?ex=69ccfa0d&is=69cba88d&hm=2d649b9f9c5f0b76344613f9dff52214b81fc4ed64b3b3e53bb7db4c662af280&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426524158187278338", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 新伙计-The Newcomer-**\n\n提高警惕，不是只有老伙计会用靴子狠狠踢你的……排球。\nStay alert. Not just your old pal will lay the boot into you... your volleyball.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:57:42.849000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426524157553672216", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1430952, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524157553672216/3.jpg?ex=69ccfa26&is=69cba8a6&hm=451488ba886acf5690be118b43fc9239061da5e03d85e6820234eda554cb1ba6&"}, {"id": "1426524157935485121", "filename": "03._-The_Newcomer-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 21146902, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524157935485121/03._-The_Newcomer-.wav?ex=69ccfa26&is=69cba8a6&hm=7e0bfc3ef42a71121037717a096e1f1f881825aa85e04b570734363a8cd36077&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426524233063993485", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 美德骑士与巨魔-Knight and Maniac-**\n\n「骑士精神」队，有1/4的骑士精神，和3/4的战斗狂魔。\nThe \"Chivalry\" is made up of one-quarter chivalry and three-quarters battle mania.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:58:00.701000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426524231969148978", "filename": "04._-Knight_and_Maniac-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28548076, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524231969148978/04._-Knight_and_Maniac-.wav?ex=69ccfa38&is=69cba8b8&hm=0ef9fb924149c94733fda5e40fe3cc743e407d72c4920e8373e50dcfd8310bd7&"}, {"id": "1426524232518729801", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1458958, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524232518729801/4.jpg?ex=69ccfa38&is=69cba8b8&hm=f977fc6ba623afc252d6fe6c94b2f8f0e28e22ce28c661e62f73efb7db65c820&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426524450064564224", "channel_id": "1426523827449626745", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 坠落的太阳-Sun's Descent-**\n\n如果第一幕出现了一支枪，它在最后就会响。\n你已经构思好重逢时，要向她诉说的故事。\n那是一个梦，梦的开始坠落了一枚明亮的太阳，梦的结局坠落了一枚漆黑的太阳。\n\nIf there is a gun in the first act, it must go off in the last.\nYou've already conceived the story to tell her when you meet again.\nIt was a dream: one that started with a brilliant sun's descent and ended with a pitch-black sun's fall.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T10:58:52.438000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426524449284427942", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1447317, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524449284427942/6.jpg?ex=69ccfa6c&is=69cba8ec&hm=a574e83877c46b5601e4a5dd72c6f460831f09cab147c8fd8a1fc6e17c3f2a13&"}, {"id": "1426524449758249000", "filename": "06._-Suns_Descent-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 48468496, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426523827449626745/1426524449758249000/06._-Suns_Descent-.wav?ex=69ccfa6c&is=69cba8ec&hm=0f2a7049680916a45094cd957ec9ee78ebbd105ec0a8b6635f3020891aec56e5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426523827449626745", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：永无乡假日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
